<title>TURKEY: Turkey's Turkcell secures $575-mln loan - company.</title>
<headline>Turkey's Turkcell secures $575-mln loan - company.</headline>
<dateline>ISTANBUL 1997-07-31</dateline>
<text>
<p>Turkey's leading GSM operator Turkcell said it had secured a $575 million project financing facility.</p>
<p>&quot;Turkcell has secured a foreign loan of $575 million. $200 million of this loan will used to finance licence and $375 million for infrastructure investments,&quot; the company said in a statement.</p>
<p>It did not give any further detail.</p>
</text>
